data.description: Welcome to your cozy retreat in the heart of King! This charming one-story home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, and attached 2 car garage offering the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover the new flooring throughout, and spacious living area with vaulted ceilings, creating an airy and open feel The kitchen features ample counter space and a convenient layout for easy meal preparation. Step outside onto the deck, where you can soak up the sunshine in your backyard or garden. A storage building provides ample space for storing outdoor equipment, while the paved drive offers convenient parking. New vapor barrier in crawlspace. Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, while still providing a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle.
